Titolo: RollerGames (video game)

Anno: 1990

Descrizione: Rollergames is the name of two 1990 Konami video games, one a coin-operated arcade game by, the other a Nintendo Entertainment System game, and both based on the television show of the same name.  This arcade game is faithful to the show unlike the NES version of RollerGames, which is a side-scrolling game.  The game is for two players and features all the skaters and managers from the league.